Key Match Events: Tim Southee took 3-31 to skittle Australia for 111
Devon Conway starred for New Zealand with 92 off 58
Neesham added late impetus with 26 off 13
Lockie Ferguson's 42 off 16 got New Zealand off to a flying start
Post-Match Reflections: Andrew Moore stated, 'The story out of this is the brilliant performance from New Zealand.'
Stuart Clark commented, 'There is some soul searching to do for the Australians. The tournament isn't over but they are going to have to improve their performances.'
